data.description: Have you dreamed of living in "The Village"? Experience the practicality of hardwood floors. The workshop boasts multiple uses, providing the opportunity to unleash your creativity and engage in various practical endeavors. The primary bedroom has a sliding door that opens up to a private porch. Immerse yourself in the Oregon weather on the wrap-around deck. Need some extra storage space? No worries, there's a basement for that. For those days when you come home tired, there's a convenient mudroom to keep your mess contained. This cozy "Village" cottage is the perfect place to call home. [Home Energy Score = 3. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10219685]
